body_html:
This behavior no longer happens in tensorflow-nightly-20170816:

$ python -c 'import tensorflow as tf; tf.Session().run(tf.square(0))'
2017-08-16 09:48:29.949554: I tensorflow/core/platform/cpu_feature_guard.cc:137] Your CPU supports instructions that this TensorFlow binary was not compiled to use: SSE4.1 SSE4.2 AVX AVX2 FMA

Build 591 has the bug, while build 592 does not. The diff is d480ac5...3686ef0.

From the commit description, I suspect that 9e6183e fixed this.

body:
This behavior no longer happens in tensorflow-nightly-20170816:
```
$ python -c 'import tensorflow as tf; tf.Session().run(tf.square(0))'
2017-08-16 09:48:29.949554: I tensorflow/core/platform/cpu_feature_guard.cc:137] Your CPU supports instructions that this TensorFlow binary was not compiled to use: SSE4.1 SSE4.2 AVX AVX2 FMA
```
Build 591 has the bug, while build 592 does not. The diff is d480ac587a0040acfc21bc2f63faa12cfd3194cc...3686ef0d51047d2806df3e2ff6c1aac727456c1d.

From the commit description, I suspect that 9e6183e4a fixed this.
